cast.overview: Ex-hitman John Wick comes out of retirement to track down the gangsters that took everything from him.
cast.title: John Wick

details.biography: Nadia Kay is a Brooklyn-raised actress and singer who toured the East Coast of the United States for several years with recorded performances at the legendary NYC venues -Bitter End, Crash Mansion and others. After appearing in major studio productions including action thriller 'John Wick' (Lionsgate) and 'Vinyl' TV Series (FOX), Nadia decided to change direction and pursue a career in film and TV.
details.name: Nadia Kay
